```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Flutterwave
    participant Gateway
    participant Payments
    participant Ledger
    participant Accounts

    Flutterwave->>Gateway: POST /payments/webhooks/provider (SUCCESS)
    Gateway->>Payments: webhook(reference, status)
    Payments->>Ledger: post(transactionId)
    Ledger-->>Payments: Posted ledger transaction
    Payments->>Accounts: publish balance update event
    Accounts-->>Payments: ACK
    Payments-->>Gateway: 202 Accepted
    Gateway-->>Flutterwave: 202 Accepted
```
